OL,3,CMPs warn chancellor 'not to cave in to
OL,4,Cindustry scaremongering' on gambling
OL,5,Ctax
OL,7,FBy ITV News Business Editor Joel Hills
OL,8,Fand ITV News Senior Producer Jack Abbey
OL,10,FMPs on the Treasury Select Committee
OL,11,Fhave accused betting firms of
OL,12,Fexaggerating the damage that higher
OL,13,Ftaxes would cause to the industry.
OL,15,FIn a report, published ahead of the
OL,16,FBudget, they urge the government "not
OL,17,Fto cave in to industry scaremongering".
OL,19,FTaxes on the industry should properly
OL,20,Freflect the social harm some forms of
OL,21,Fgambling cause, the Committee says.
