OL,4,Cindustry scaremongering' on gambling
OL,5,Ctax
OL,7,F"Whether at a local race track or a
OL,8,Fseaside arcade, for many people
OL,9,Fgambling is a fun pastime enjoyed with
OL,10,Ffamily and friends," says Dame Meg
OL,11,FHillier, the chair of the committee
OL,13,FShe added: "For too many people, the
OL,14,Fhighly addictive and harmful nature of
OL,15,Fonline betting games has seriously
OL,16,Fimpacted their lives and the lives of
OL,17,Fthose around them."
