OL,4,Cindustry scaremongering' on gambling
OL,5,Ctax
OL,7,FThe Institute for Public Policy
OL,8,FResearch (IPPR) estimates that the
OL,9,Fgovernment could raise an extra #3.2
OL,10,Fbillion a year by increasing taxes on
OL,11,Fonline gambling, physical slot
OL,12,Fmachines and sports betting.
OL,14,FFormer prime minister Gordon Brown has
OL,15,Fbacked the proposal, saying the money
OL,16,Fshould be used to lift the cap on
OL,17,Fbenefits for families with more than
OL,18,Ftwo children.
