OL,5,Ctax
OL,7,FThe Betting and Gaming Council (BGC)
OL,8,Fsays increasing remote Gaming Duty
OL,9,Ffrom 21% to 50%, machines gaming duty
OL,10,Ffrom 20% to 50% and general betting
OL,11,Fduty from 15% to 25% would raise far
OL,12,Fless than the IPPR assumes - driving
OL,13,Fpeople to bet with unlicensed, black-
OL,14,Fmarket operators.
OL,16,FAnalysis by EY, commissioned by the
OL,17,Findustry, concluded tax rises on this
OL,18,Fscale would also risk the loss of up
OL,19,Fto 40,000 jobs.
