OL,7,F"Online betting games are extracting
OL,8,Fhuge amounts of money from people who
OL,9,Fhave been funnelled into the most
OL,10,Faddictive, harmful corners of the
OL,11,Findustry via their love of sports, or
OL,12,Fthe occasional game of bingo," said
OL,13,FMeg Hillier.
