OL,7,FBetting and Gaming Council (BGC) chief
OL,8,Fexecutive Grainne Hurst said: "Further
OL,9,Ftax increases on the regulated online
OL,10,Fsector risk undermining consumer
OL,11,Fprotections by pushing players towards
OL,12,Fthe unsafe, unregulated black market `
OL,13,Fwhile reducing Treasury revenues and
OL,14,Fcutting the vital funding our members
OL,15,Fprovide to British sport, including
OL,16,Fhorse racing, football, rugby league,
OL,17,Fdarts and snooker.
