OL,3,CMPs warn chancellor 'not to cave in to
OL,4,Cindustry scaremongering' on gambling
OL,5,Ctax
OL,7,F"We have always recognised that
OL,8,Fbetting and gaming can lead to harm
OL,9,Ffor a small minority, which is why our
OL,10,Fmembers are investing more than ever
OL,11,Fin safer gambling ` including new
OL,12,Fstake limits on online gaming,
OL,13,Fenhanced affordability checks, swift
OL,14,Fdata-driven interventions, robust
OL,15,Fadvertising safeguards, and funding
OL,16,Ffor a new #100 million statutory levy
OL,17,Ffor research, prevention, and
OL,18,Ftreatment to tackle problem gambling
OL,19,Fand related harm."
